thor TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.36</biblScope></bibl>, etc.: hence to reckon <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">exactly</tr_> or <pb n=\"2023\" TEIform=\"pb\"/> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">accurately,</tr_> opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀπὸ χειρὸς λ.,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:656\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">656</biblScope> </bibl> (anap.); <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐ τιθεὶς ψήφους</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg018.perseus-grc1:229\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.229</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐν ψήφῳ λέγειν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg005.perseus-grc1:570\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ag.\">Ag.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">570</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐν ψήφου λόγῳ θέσθαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg019.perseus-grc1:309\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Rh.\">Rh.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">309</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: metaph., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ταῖς τοῦ συμφέροντος ψήφοις μετρεῖν τὰς ἔχθρας καὶ τὰς φιλίας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:47:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.47.5</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: hence <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ψῆφος</foreign> itself for a <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cipher, number,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πὸτ ἄρτιον</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀριθμὸν</foreign>)<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ποτθέμειν . . ψᾶφον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0521.tlg001:170\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Epich.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">170</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: pl., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">accounts,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">καθαραὶ ψ.,</foreign> where there is an exact balance, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg018.perseus-grc1:227\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.227</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οἱ περὶ τὰς ψ.</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">calculators,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0640.tlg001:1:26\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Alciphr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.26</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ψήφων ἄπειρος</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.812e</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δακτυλικὴ ψ.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">reckoning</tr_> on the fingers, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.290</biblScope> </bibl> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=